1. *Sličiš* na svoju majku. (You resemble your mother.)
2. Ova slika *liči* na onu koju smo videli juče. (This picture looks like the one we saw yesterday.)
3. *Slici* mi taj oblik na papiru. (Draw that shape for me on the paper.)
4. Ta situacija *ne sliči* ničemu što smo ranije videli. (This situation doesn't resemble anything we've seen before.)
5. *Slično* iskustvo sam imao pre nekoliko godina. (I had a similar experience a few years ago.)
6. On *liči* na osobu koju sam upoznao pre par godina. (He looks like the person I met a few years ago.)
7. *Sličan* problem sam imao pre mesec dana. (I had a similar problem a month ago.)
8. Ova haljina *ne sliči* onoj koju sam naručila. (This dress doesn't look like the one I ordered.)
9. Ona *liči* na svoju sestru bliznakinju. (She looks like her twin sister.)
10. *Slično* razmišljanje imamo o tom pitanju. (We have a similar way of thinking about that issue.)